  "detailed_description": "Easy to pick up, and hard to put down! Parry Nightmare is a one-of-a-kind \"parry heaven\" action game where the best offense is a good defense!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081230/extras/2696e3dee0274be0336dcd5492c6ff14.poster.avif?t=1752821619\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081230/extras/2696e3dee0274be0336dcd5492c6ff14.webm?t=1752821619\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081230/extras/2696e3dee0274be0336dcd5492c6ff14.mp4?t=1752821619\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Use your nightmare's strength against it with your trusty parry move! Stun foes, send away projectiles, and stop threats right in their tracks by chaining parries!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081230/extras/734df77e3b34851a73a2e66ed53f4d75.poster.avif?t=1752821619\" width=400 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081230/extras/734df77e3b34851a73a2e66ed53f4d75.webm?t=1752821619\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081230/extras/734df77e3b34851a73a2e66ed53f4d75.mp4?t=1752821619\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Honno-chan will defeat any foes you stun automatically. Leave them to her and focus on the defense!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081230/extras/c9714b3a94595a59960731975b147f50.poster.avif?t=1752821619\" width=500 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081230/extras/c9714b3a94595a59960731975b147f50.webm?t=1752821619\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081230/extras/c9714b3a94595a59960731975b147f50.mp4?t=1752821619\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Parrying grants your soul more and more courage to face the night! Heal up by continuing to parry! Spend excess soul to unleash a powerful Burst move to wipe out hordes of enemies at once!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081230/extras/a1b865cb78d192325653af24bd1308a6.poster.avif?t=1752821619\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081230/extras/a1b865cb78d192325653af24bd1308a6.webm?t=1752821619\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081230/extras/a1b865cb78d192325653af24bd1308a6.mp4?t=1752821619\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Collect powerups from rare foes to supercharge Honno-chan! Breathe fire, deploy orbital pain, wreak havoc, and more!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081230/extras/c695a79c25ad8dd37dd17abb71b561bf.poster.avif?t=1752821619\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081230/extras/c695a79c25ad8dd37dd17abb71b561bf.webm?t=1752821619\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081230/extras/c695a79c25ad8dd37dd17abb71b561bf.mp4?t=1752821619\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Defeated enemies drop light. Collect light and the darkness of the nightmare abates, giving you a clearer view of the chaos. Max out your light meter to beat the nightmare!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081230/extras/1951f16f2b774997d4b797ad9989600f.poster.avif?t=1752821619\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081230/extras/1951f16f2b774997d4b797ad9989600f.webm?t=1752821619\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081230/extras/1951f16f2b774997d4b797ad9989600f.mp4?t=1752821619\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Will you be able to escape the nightmare and greet a new day...?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081230/extras/bc9ccf6a28100bf11529c1ea81382747.poster.avif?t=1752821619\" width=522 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081230/extras/bc9ccf6a28100bf11529c1ea81382747.webm?t=1752821619\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2081230/extras/bc9ccf6a28100bf11529c1ea81382747.mp4?t=1752821619\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
